list-item.p:
Frequency – the average of the instantaneous frequency of the burst event. Instantaneous frequency inst_freq_ch_day was calculated by computing:


the differentiated unwrapped phase of the complex valued signal (after the Hilbert transform using np.angle, np.unwrap, np.diff), yielding dphase_ch_day

normalizing the phase: inst_freq_ch_day = dphase_ch_day * (1 / 0.5*pi) * fs;
